reviewText: In this movie you will learn about early native Indian tribes, Spanish settlers, wildlife, native plants, fruit, and food!  You will learn about wars and will see crafts made and then sold in the USA!  You will also hear A lot of native music this and you will learn much much more!
BOUGHT FOR MY PI- AMERICAN LADY. SHE LOVES IT.
It's very hard to find travel videos on the Philippines.  This VHS tape is part of the Video Visits series.  It's a pretty good video, I just wish they would update it and put it on DVD.
